2 AN ACT TO ELIMINATE THE TRAINING COURSE REQUIREMENTS FOR INSURANCE
3 PRODUCER LICENSURE, TO CLARIFY THE APPLICABILITY OF THE CAP ON
4 INSURANCE REFERRAL FEES PAID TO NONLICENSED PERSONS, TO MAINTAIN
